  displayTitle: Crocodile Moon
  theme: 1
  openingStory: 'Three lagoon crocodiles have also noticed the gem. Their treasure
    policy is simple: if it glows, chomp near it.'
  successStory: Three moonlit jaws miss by heroic margins. The crocodiles file a
    strongly worded splash.
  lessonText: Read each warning ripple and keep one boost ready. Recovery food follows
    every ambush.
  failureHintText: Do not boost at the first bubble. Use the bright warning ripple
    as your cue.
